{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"itemid","mdn_url":"/es/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes/itemid","locale":"es","native":"Español","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"resumen","title":"Resumen","isH3":false,"content":"<p>El atributo <strong>Itemid </strong>es un identificador global y único de un item.</p>\n\n<p>Los atributos Itemid attributes sólo se pueden especificar en elmentos que tiene atributos tanto de <strong>itemscope </strong>como&nbsp;<strong>itemtype</strong>. Además, el&nbsp;itemid sólo puede ser especficiado en elemento con un atributo&nbsp;itemscope cuyo correspondiente itemtype hace referencia o define un vocabulario que soporte identificadores globales.</p>\n\n<p>Un vocabulario de itemtype nos proporcionará el significado exacto de un identificador global definido dentro del vocabulario.&nbsp;El vocabulario definirá si varios item con el mismo identificador global puede co-existir y, si están permitidos, cómo item con el mismo identificador son gestionados.</p>\n\n<p class=\"note\"><strong>Nota:</strong>&nbsp;La definición de &nbsp;itemid hecha por Whatwg.org dice que debe ser una URL. No parece que sea el caso de el ejemplo que se muestra más abajo.&nbsp;Sin embargo la definición de facto es que un itemid es un identificador único, así que los apropiado es URB.&nbsp;Esta inconsistencia refleja sin dudarlo la naturaleza incompleta de la espeficicación Microdata.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ejemplo","title":"Ejemplo","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html","title":"HTML","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dl</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">itemscope</span>\n    <span class=\"token attr-name\">itemtype</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://vocab.example.net/book<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token attr-name\">itemid</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>urn:isbn:0-330-34032-8<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Título <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dd</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">itemprop</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>titulo<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>The Reality Dysfunction\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Autor <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dd</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">itemprop</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>autor<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Peter F. Hamilton\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Fecha de publicación\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dd</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>time</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">itemprop</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>fechapublicacion<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">datetime</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>26-01-1996<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>26 Enero 1996<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>time</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>dl</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"datos_estructurados","title":"Datos estructurados","isH3":true,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"14\">itemscope</td>\n   <td>itemtype: itemid</td>\n   <td colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n    <div class=\"jyrRxf-eEDwDf jcd3Mb IZ65Hb-hUbt4d\" id=\"sect1\"><span>http://vocab.example.net/book</span>: urn:isbn:0-330-34032-8</div>\n   </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>itemprop</td>\n   <td><span>titulo</span></td>\n   <td><span>The Reality Dysfunction</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>itemprop</td>\n   <td><span>autor</span></td>\n   <td>\n    <div class=\"jyrRxf-eEDwDf jcd3Mb\" id=\"sect2\"><span>Peter F. Hamilton</span></div>\n   </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>itemprop</td>\n   <td><span>fechapublicacion</span></td>\n   <td><span>26-01-1996</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"resultado","title":"Resultado","isH3":true,"content":"<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"HTML sample\" id=\"frame_html\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/es/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes/itemid/_sample_.html.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificaciones","title":"Especificaciones","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\" style=\"height: 105px; width: 490px;\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificación</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Estad</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/microdata.html#attr-itemid\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">itemid</a></td>\n   <td>Nota WG - No está siendo ya activamente desarrollado.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Resumen","id":"resumen"},{"text":"Ejemplo","id":"ejemplo"},{"text":"Especificaciones","id":"especificaciones"}],"summary":"El atributo Itemid es un identificador global y único de un item.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"itemid","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"itemid","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"itemid","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"itemid","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"itemid","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"itemid","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"es/web/html/global_attributes/itemid","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/es/web/html/global_attributes/itemid/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/es/docs/Web","title":"Tecnología para desarrolladores web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML: Lenguaje de etiquetas de hipertexto"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes","title":"Atributos globales"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes/itemid","title":"itemid"}],"pageTitle":"itemid - HTML: Lenguaje de etiquetas de hipertexto | MDN","noIndexing":false}}